1 A BILL for an Act to amend and reenact section 20.1-01-34 of the North Dakota Century Code,
2 relating to deer hunting with a crossbow.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Section 20.1-01-34 of the North Dakota Century Code is
5 amended and reenacted as follows:
6 20.1-01-34. Crossbow legal weapon.
7 1. Notwithstanding any other provision of law, an individual may use a crossbow during
8 the duration of any deer gun season if the individual possesses the appropriate deer
9 gun license.
10 2. An individual over the age of seventy-five may use a crossbow during the duration of
11 any deer bow season if the individual possesses the appropriate deer bow license.
